(7, 'document', 'text/html', 'FAQS', 'FAQS', 'FAQS', 'faqs', 'FAQS', 1, 0, 0, 3, 0, 'Get the answers to some common questions asked by website users...', '<h2 class="dec">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\r\n<p>We haven''t had a huge amount of questions asked as yet but here''s a few that may help. Please feel free and contact us at support [at] theweddingwebsitegroup.com with any questions you might have.</p>\r\n<div id="faqs">\r\n<h3>Are there any additional charges other than the initial purchase price?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>No, the price you pay is for the package you choose and lasts for one year only. You will need to contact us if you wanted to extend beyond the year.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Do I get a free .co.uk or .com domain with my website?</h3>\r\n<div class="justifyright">\r\n<p>Your Free domain name will be an appendage of the ''TheWeddingWebsiteGroup.com''.<br />So for instance if you want to have ''alex-and-jo'' the domain name would be ''weddingwebsitesuk.co.uk/alex-and-jo.<br />If you do want your own personal domain name , we can buy this for you, please email to <strong>support [at] theweddingwebsitegroup.com</strong> stating what domain name you would like and we can forward details of costs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Can I have more space to enable me to have more photographs on my website?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Yes we have 3 packages that should suffice for most people. The top package allows 1000MB of space. This equates to around 300+ photos if each photo is 3MB.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>I am concerned about any personal information on my website appearing on the search engines,  can i prevent my site from appearing in a web search?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Yes. You have the option to prevent search engines from indexing your website. You can also password protect the entire site or individual pages.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>How can i make a suggestion for the website?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Please contact <strong>suggestions [at] theweddingwebsitegroup.com</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>How can i report a problem?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Please contact <strong>support [at] theweddingwebsitegroup.com</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>How many photos can i upload to my website?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>It depends on the physical file size of each photo. If each photo is 3MB (typical size) then the basic package of 200MB would allow for approximately 66 images. However your photos may only be 1MB each in which case you could have up to 200 photos with the basic package.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /faq-styles -->\r\n<script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\r\n	$(document).ready(function() {\r\n  $(''#faqs h3'').each(function() {\r\n    var tis = $(this), state = false, answer = tis.next(''div'').hide().css(''height'',''auto'').slideUp();\r\n    tis.click(function() {\r\n      state = !state;\r\n      answer.slideToggle(state);\r\n      tis.toggleClass(''active'',state);\r\n    });\r\n  });\r\n});\r\n// ]]></script>', 1, 42, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1299013700, 1, 1324383568, 0, 0, 0, 1299013680, 1, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(8, 'document', 'text/html', 'Contact', 'Contact', 'Contact', 'contact', 'Contact', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '<h2 class="dec">We''re here to help</h2>\r\n<p>Couldn''t find an answer in our FAQ section or want to know more about The Weddimg Website Group?<br />Complete the form below and we''ll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>\r\n<form id="EmailForm" action="[[~[[*id]]]]" method="post">\r\n<fieldset>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><label for="cfName">Your name: <span class="invalidValue">[[+fi.error.name]]</span></label> <input id="cfName" class="text" name="name:required" type="text" value="[[+fi.name]]" /> </li>\r\n<li><label for="cfEmail">Your Email Address: <span class="invalidValue">[[+fi.error.email]]</span> </label><input id="cfEmail" class="text" name="email:required:email" type="text" value="[[+fi.email]]" /> </li>\r\n<li><label for="cfMessage">Message: <span class="invalidValue">[[+fi.error.message]]</span> </label><textarea id="cfMessage" cols="20" rows="4" name="message:required:stripTags">[[+fi.message]]</textarea> </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</fieldset>\r\n <fieldset class="submit">\r\n <input id="cfContact" class="submit-buy" name="submitContact" type="submit" value="Send enquiry" /> \r\n</fieldset>\r\n</form>\r\n<div class="divider-690"> We are a UK based company tucked away in Bradford in the north of England. We currently do not have a contact number for any enquiries but you can be sure to get a quick response from using the above form or contacting us directly <a href="mailto:info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com">here</a></div>', 1, 2, 10, 1, 0, 1, 1299013717, 1, 1335535360, 0, 0, 0, 1299013680, 1, 'Contact', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(10, 'document', 'text/html', 'Archives', 'Archives', 'Archives', 'archives', 'Archives', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '[[!getPage?\n  &element=`getArchives`\n  &elementClass=`modSnippet`\n  &tpl=`blogPost`\n  &hideContainers=`1`\n  &pageVarKey=`page`\n  &parents=`6`\n  &includeTVs=`1`\n  &toPlaceholder=`archives`\n  &limit=`10`\n  &cache=`0`\n]]\n \n<h3>[[+arc_month_name]] [[+arc_year]] Archives</h3>\n \n[[+archives]]\n \n[[!+page.nav:notempty=`\n<div class="paging"> \n<ul class="pageList"> \n  [[!+page.nav]] \n</ul> \n</div>\n`]]\n\n[[!userGetWebsiteFromURL]]', 1, 2, 12, 1, 0, 1, 1299183600, 3, 1333528699, 0, 0, 0, 1299183600, 1, 'Archives', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(11, 'document', 'text/html', 'blog test post', 'blog test post', 'blog test post', 'blog-test-post', 'blog test post', 1, 0, 0, 6, 0, 'Some intro text for the footer latest', 'In the 1950s, the art establishment had a rather narrow view of art and art history. When abstract art was at its peak, Hudson River School paintings by Frederick Church and Albert Bierstadt were considered too realistic, too tightly painted and photographic and were often deacessioned by museums and largely ignored by collectors. Similarly, William Bouguereau was customarily derided in art-history lectures. Then along came an artistic revolution; starting with Pop Art and Andy Warhol—who owned a painting by Bouguereau—the canons of art started to broaden.', 1, 3, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1299184142, 1, 1302622502, 0, 0, 0, 1296592140, 1, 'blog test post', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(12, 'document', 'text/html', 'blog test post 1', 'blog test post 1', 'blog test post 1', 'blog-test-post-1', 'blog test post 1', 1, 0, 0, 6, 0, 'introtext to go in the footer area...two lines would be sufficient', '<p>Typography is an essential component of a website’s design. This is for good reason: good typography is not only imperative for aesthetic appeal, but also improves site usability when text legibility and readability concepts are applied. Typography is all about proportions and spacing. There are also font styles to consider</p>', 1, 3, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1299185859, 1, 1324323624, 0, 0, 0, 1299185820, 1, 'blog test post 1', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
