(38, 'document', 'text/html', 'Easy Admin Panel', 'Easy Admin Panel', 'Easy Admin Panel', '', 'Easy Admin Panel', 1, 0, 0, 3, 0, 'Make as many updates to your website as you like from an easy to use admin area...', '<h2 class="dec">Easy Admin Panel</h2>\r\n<p class="p-bigger">Once you’ve signed up for your wedding website you will be able to log in to your admin panel and start adding content and updating the pre-defined pages.</p>\r\n<p><img class="justifyright" title="wedding website feature tour" src="assets/templates/wedding/images/img-placeholder-tour.gif" alt="wedding website feature tour" width="453" height="215" />The main menu for your website pages is on the left of your admin pages. We have pre selected the 20 most popular titles to get you started. You have a choice to change the titles, turn the pages on or off and password protect individual pages.</p>\r\n<p>You can easily add content whether it be plain text, images or hyperlinks. The editor contains the most popular formatting options such as making text bold, italic or creating headings.</p>', 1, 42, 2, 1, 0, 1, 1315518327, 1, 1324376801, 0, 0, 0, 1315518360, 1, 'Easy Admin Panel', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
