(1805, 'document', 'text/html', 'Home', 'general', 'home', 'home', 'home', 1, 0, 0, 1804, 0, '', '<h3>Welcome to our wedding website!</h3>\n<p>\n<br />\n<img class="justifyleft" src="assets/templates/wedding/wed-themes/images/img-home.jpg" alt="" width="251" height="187" /></p>\n<p>Hi everyone.</p>\n<p>Here''s our very own Wedding Website! You will find all the details you need about our wedding day. Come back often as we will keep posting updates, pictures, events, and other content to keep you all in the loop.</p>\n<p>It is hard to believe we have been in a relationship for almost 7 years. 7 years!! I''m sure this 7th year will be one that keeps us on our toes getting ready for our big day.</p>\n<p>Don''t know forget to RSVP if you still haven''t done so. You can also share your thoughts or comments about us in our wedding guestbook.</p>\n<p>We have added a gift list for anyone who insists on getting us a present and you can find out where to stay if you are travelling the miles to be with us.</p>\n<p>All this journey has been fun and we thought it will be a good idea to share this with you...</p>\n<p>We hope you enjoy it as much as we have.</p>', 1, 37, 0, 1, 0, 1, 1336126513, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Home', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
