(1729, 'document', 'text/html', 'Gift List', 'general', 'Gift List', 'gift-list', 'Gift List', 1, 0, 0, 1720, 0, '', '<p>As we have pretty much everything a young couple could need we have decided we shouldn''t ask friends and family for gifts. However we are aware that some friends and family are insistant so therefore we have asked that donations be made to the following charitable organizations...</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href="http://www.webpods.co.uk">Charity 1</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.webpods.co.uk">Charity 2</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.webpods.co.uk">Charity 3</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>We would like to thank you for making a donation and if that''s not enough for you kind folk you can always buy us a drink;-)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 37, 8, 1, 0, 137, 1335975171, 0, 0, 1, 1336125840, 1, 0, 0, 'Gift List', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
