(165, 'userInvitesMail', '', 0, 53, 0, '<p>Hello [[+guestName]], [[+userPartner1]] and [[+userPartner2]] are pleased to invite you to the [[+eventName]] event for their forthcoming wedding on [[+userWeddingDate]].</p>\n<p>The [[+eventName]] will take place from [[+eventStart]] until [[+eventEnd]] on [[+eventDate]].</p>\n<p>The location of the event is :- <br/>\n    [[+eventAddress1]]<br/>\n    [[+eventAddress2]]<br/>\n    [[+eventAddress3]]<br/>\n    [[+eventAddress4]]<br/>\n<p>Please click the following link to RSVP this event.</p>\n<br/>\n[[+eventPageLink]]\n<br/>\n<p>For future reference your unique guest identifier is [[+guestIdentifier]].</p>\n<p>Please telephone this number [[+userTel]] if you have any questions.</p>\n<p>Thank you from  [[+userPartner1]] and [[+userPartner2]].</p>', 0, NULL),
