u may add or delete images from the core/components/captcha/noise directory\r\nas long as there is at least one file there.\r\n\r\nCaptcha can also be used in other forms that require captcha.\r\n\r\nYou can roll your own function by calling assets/components/captcha/captcha.php where you want the image\r\nand then comparing the user''s input to the $_SESSION[''veriword''] variable.\r\n\r\nSee the code in the core/components/captcha/captcha.plugin.php file.\r\n";s:9:"changelog";s:781:"Changelog for Captcha.\r\n\r\nCaptcha 3.2.4\r\n - Fixed bug with failed validator\r\n\r\nCaptcha 3.2.3\r\n - Fixed bug in Transport Package\r\n\r\nCaptcha 3.2.2\r\n - Updated PhpDoc comments\r\n - Added changelog.txt\r\n - Added readme.md\r\n - Reorganized for Git\r\n - Revolution Transport Package updated\r\n - Converted tabs to spaces\r\n\r\nCaptcha 3.2.1\r\n - Test for Necessary GD and FreeType functions on install\r\n\r\n\r\nCaptcha 3.1.0\r\n - Updated for Revolution RC3\r\n - Fixed bug with captcha words\r\n - Converted $modx->config calls to getOption()\r\n\r\nCaptcha 3.0.3\r\n - Fixed bugs in build script\r\n - Moved target directory\r\n - Added license and readme\r\n\r\n Captcha 3.0.2\r\n - $_SESSION mathstring value can override system setting\r\n - Updates to build script\r\n\r\n Captcha 3.0.1\r\n - First Revolution release\r\n\r\n\r\n";s:13:"setup-options";s:0:"";s:6:"action";s:7:"install";s:9:"signature";s:19:"captcha-3.2.4-beta1";s:8:"register";s:3:"mgr";s:5:"topic";s:47:"/workspace/package/install/captcha-3.2.4-beta1/";s:12:"HTTP_MODAUTH";s:27:"modx4e5e11c08bfb55.31199375";}', 'captcha', 'a:31:{i:0;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:2:"id";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:24:"4d556c28b2b083396d000a3c";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:1;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:7:"package";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:24:"4d556c28b2b083396d000a3c";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:2;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:12:"display_name";s:10:"attributes";a:0:{}s:4:"text";s:19:"captcha-3.2.4-beta1";s:8:"children";a:0:{}}i:3;a:4:{s:4:"name"